      "rationale": "Three-mesh Richardson extrapolation study conducted: coarse (2.1M cells), medium (6.8M cells), fine (18.4M cells). Grid convergence index (GCI) for NIH: GCI_fine = 2.3%, GCI_medium = 7.1%. Asymptotic range ratio = 1.02, confirming convergence. Production simulations use fine mesh. Time-step refinement study confirms temporal discretization error < 0.5% for NIH.",
