      "rationale": "All model inputs characterised with probability distributions: inlet velocity profile (log-normal, CV 5%), blood viscosity (normal, CV 8%), hemolysis model coefficients (uniform bounds ±12% per literature range), wall roughness (triangular, 0.2–0.8 μm). Input distributions validated against independent measurements. Total of 11 uncertain inputs propagated through Monte Carlo ensemble (N=2000). Input sensitivity documented via Sobol indices; dominant inputs identified as hemolysis exponent (S₁=0.62) and blood viscosity (S₁=0.18).",
